@{
    ViewBag.Title = "最新消息";
    ViewBag.Title2 = "台灣優靈客協會第一屆第二次會員大會暨會員親子日";
    ViewBag.BodyClass = "News";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/Layout.cshtml";
    ViewBag.customShareInfo = false;
}

<h2 class="sr-only">@ViewBag.Title</h2>

<section id="content">

    <div id="banner">
        <h2 class="h3 wrap">
            <span class="title">@ViewBag.Title</span>
        </h2>
        <img class="thumb" src="~/Content/images/News/banner.jpg" alt="">
    </div>

    <div class="wrap">

        <ul class="breadcrumb text-md-right">
            <li><a href="~/Index">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="~/News/List">@ViewBag.Title</a></li>
            <li>最新消息內容</li>
        </ul>

        <article class="article section">
            <h4 class="h4">@ViewBag.Title2</h4>
            <h5 class="h5"><small><i class="ti-calendar"></i> 2017-06-01</small></h5>
            <div class="editor main-text">
                <p>本協會謹訂於106年6月4日(星期日)上午10時假郭元益糕餅博物館(楊梅館)，舉辦「台灣優靈客協會第一屆第二次會員大會暨會員親子日」活動。</p>
                <p>活動流程：</p>
                <table class="table table-striped">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>時間</th>
                            <th>內容</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>09:30 - 10:00</td>
                            <td>報到</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>10:00 - 10:10</td>
                            <td>主席致詞</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>10:10 - 10:30</td>
                            <td>長官/貴賓致詞</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>10:30 - 12:00</td>
                            <td>會員大會/眷屬主題活動</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>12:00 - 13:00</td>
                            <td>餐敘交流</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>13:00 - 14:30</td>
                            <td>親子家庭日活動</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>14:30 - </td>
                            <td>自由活動</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </article>

        <p class="text-xs-center">
            <a href="~/News/List" class="btn btn-primary">回列表</a>
        </p>
        
    </div>

</section>

